{"quotes": [{"lines": [{"text": "I'll be there... around every corner... in every empty room... as inevitable as your guilty conscience...", "character": "The Shadow", "characterId": "nm0000285"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "Oh, God I dreamed.", "character": "Margo Lane", "characterId": "nm0000542"}, {"text": "So did I. What did you dream?", "character": "Lamont Cranston", "characterId": "nm0000285"}, {"text": "I was lying naked on a beach in the South Seas. The tide was coming up to my toes. The sun was beating down. My skin hot and cool at the same time. It was wonderful. What was yours?", "character": "Margo Lane", "characterId": "nm0000542"}, {"text": "I dreamed I tore all the skin off my face and was somebody else underneath.", "character": "Lamont Cranston", "characterId": "nm0000285"}, {"text": "You have problems.", "character": "Margo Lane", "characterId": "nm0000542"}, {"text": "I'm aware of that.", "character": "Lamont Cranston", "characterId": "nm0000285"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "Your mind is like an open book to me!", "character": "Shiwan Khan", "characterId": "nm0518821"}, {"text": "Then learn how to read!", "character": "Lamont Cranston", "characterId": "nm0000285"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "In three days, the entire world will hear my roar, and willingly fall subject to the lost empire of Shan Kahn. That is a lovely tie, by the way. May I ask where you acquire it", "character": "Shiwan Khan", "characterId": "nm0518821"}, {"text": "Brooks Brothers.", "character": "Lamont Cranston", "characterId": "nm0000285"}, {"text": "Is that mid-town.", "character": "Shiwan Khan", "characterId": "nm0518821"}, {"text": "45th and Madison. You are a barbarian.", "character": "Lamont Cranston", "characterId": "nm0000285"}, {"text": "Thank you. We both are.", "character": "Shiwan Khan", "characterId": "nm0518821"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "We need each other.", "character": "Margo Lane", "characterId": "nm0000542"}, {"text": "No we don't.", "character": "Lamont Cranston", "characterId": "nm0000285"}, {"text": "We have a connection.", "character": "Margo Lane", "characterId": "nm0000542"}, {"text": "No we don't.", "character": "Lamont Cranston", "characterId": "nm0000285"}, {"text": "Then how can you explain that I can read your thoughts?", "character": "Margo Lane", "characterId": "nm0000542"}, {"text": "My thoughts are hard to miss.", "character": "Lamont Cranston", "characterId": "nm0000285"}, {"text": "And why is that?", "character": "Margo Lane", "characterId": "nm0000542"}, {"text": "Psychically, I'm very well endowed.", "character": "Lamont Cranston", "characterId": "nm0000285"}, {"text": "I'll bet you are.", "character": "Margo Lane", "characterId": "nm0000542"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "The weed of crime bears bitter fruit.", "character": "The Shadow", "characterId": "nm0000285"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "I saved your life, Roy Tam. It now belongs to me.", "character": "The Shadow", "characterId": "nm0000285"}, {"text": "It does?", "character": "Dr. Roy Tam", "characterId": "nm0793634"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "The clouded mind sees nothing", "character": "Tibetan Kidnapper", "characterId": "nm0661974"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "Am I in hell?", "character": "Lamont Cranston", "characterId": "nm0000285"}, {"text": "Not yet.", "character": "Tulku", "characterId": "nm0875471"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "I'll see you later", "character": "Lamont Cranston", "characterId": "nm0000285"}, {"text": "Hey, how'll you know where I am?", "character": "Margo Lane", "characterId": "nm0000542"}, {"text": "I'll know", "character": "Lamont Cranston", "characterId": "nm0000285"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "The sun is shining...", "character": "Lamont Cranston", "characterId": "nm0000285"}, {"text": "[finishing the code phrase of The Shadow]\nBut the ice is slippery.", "character": "Dr. Roy Tam", "characterId": "nm0793634"}, {"text": "You're an agent of The Shadow!", "character": "Dr. Roy Tam", "characterId": "nm0793634"}, {"text": "[feigning ignorance]\nWho?", "character": "Lamont Cranston", "characterId": "nm0000285"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "[puts a ring from the Shadow on Tam's finger]\nDon't ever take it off.", "character": "Moe Shrevnitz", "characterId": "nm0001967"}, {"text": "[confused]\nWho *are* you?", "character": "Dr. Roy Tam", "characterId": "nm0793634"}, {"text": "[holds up his hand with an identical ring on it]\nSomebody who owes him their life... somebody just like *you*.", "character": "Moe Shrevnitz", "characterId": "nm0001967"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "Oh what the heck, it's always green.", "character": "Dr. Reinhardt Lane", "characterId": "nm0005212"}, {"text": "[starts to cut the red wire]", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "NO!", "character": "Margo Lane", "characterId": "nm0000542"}, {"text": "[bomb deactivates, holds a green wire]", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "That is red! THIS is green!", "character": "Margo Lane", "characterId": "nm0000542"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "[as Lamont walks away to become The Shadow]\nWait! How will you know where I am?", "character": "Margo Lane", "characterId": "nm0000542"}, {"text": "[turns to answer]\n*I'll* know!", "character": "Lamont Cranston", "characterId": "nm0000285"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "[repeated line]", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "Somebody's coming.", "character": "Moe Shrevnitz", "characterId": "nm0001967"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "You are a barbarian.", "character": "Lamont Cranston", "characterId": "nm0000285"}, {"text": "Thank you.", "character": "Shiwan Khan", "characterId": "nm0518821"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "I guess you would call it an implosive-explosive sub-molecular device.", "character": "Dr. Roy Tam", "characterId": "nm0793634"}, {"text": "Or an Atomic Bomb.", "character": "Lamont Cranston", "characterId": "nm0000285"}, {"text": "Hey, that's catchy.", "character": "Dr. Roy Tam", "characterId": "nm0793634"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "There's a new world order coming, Shadow, and I'm going to be a king! A KING!", "character": "Farley Claymore", "characterId": "nm0000347"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "Do you have *any* *idea* who you just kidnapped?", "character": "Lamont Cranston", "characterId": "nm0000285"}, {"text": "Cranston; Lamont Cranston.", "character": "Tulku", "characterId": "nm0875471"}, {"text": "You know my real name?", "character": "Lamont Cranston", "characterId": "nm0000285"}, {"text": "Yes. I also know that for as long as you can remember, you struggled against your own black heart and always lost. You watched your sprit, your very face change as the beast claws its way out from within you. You are in great pain, aren't you?", "character": "Tulku", "characterId": "nm0875471"}, {"text": "[Cranston leaps at the Tulku, who magically vanishes and reappears]", "character": null, "characterId": null}, {"text": "You know what evil lurks in the hearts of men, for you have seen that evil in your own heart. Every man pays a price for redemption; this is yours.", "character": "Tulku", "characterId": "nm0875471"}, {"text": "I'm not lookin' for redemption!", "character": "Lamont Cranston", "characterId": "nm0000285"}, {"text": "you *will* be redeemed, because I will teach you to use your black shadow to fight evil.", "character": "Tulku", "characterId": "nm0875471"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "How did you know where to find me? How did you know who I am?", "character": "Dr. Roy Tam", "characterId": "nm0793634"}, {"text": "[begins to laugh]\nThe Shadow knows!", "character": "The Shadow", "characterId": "nm0000285"}]}]}